using graphics, turtle

	'the window' : the graphics panel
	'turtle space' : a turtle space in 'the window'

	'turtles' : a group of 16 turtles
	'turtles' speed 40
	'angle' : 0
	for each 'turtle' in 'turtles'
		'turtle' colour  (random colour)
		'turtle' heading (add 22.5 to 'angle')
		
place 'turtles' group in 'turtle space'
'turtles' pattern
hide 'turtles'

'turtles' pattern :
	repeat 10 times
		move 'turtles' (random from 200 to 400) steps
		turn 'turtles' (random from 160 to 200) degrees
